{"tid":1951380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭稱港2月零售銷售數據為歷來最大跌幅","createTime":"2020-03-31T02:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T08:40:27.000Z","uid":241764,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e0b99292aed9035a58f22c35f10c7539ef2c54","tid":1951380,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥在今早行會前見傳媒時透露，本港2月份零售銷售數據是歷來最大跌幅，並表示政府將會啟動第二輪的防疫、抗疫基金。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭指出，本港今次面對的打擊是史無前例，今日下午港府將公布的2月份零售銷售數據是有記錄以來最大跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n她說，明白香港的飲食及零售業面對的困難，感謝食肆和受影響行業的合作，政府會作出適當回應令市民能夠安心，第二輪抗疫基金會涉及數百億元。<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，早前約見地產建設商會希望減租，再次呼籲業主共渡時艱，為商戶提供租金寬免，同時要求有出租的政府部門，檢視進一步減租空間。<br />\n根據彭博調查顯示，2月零售銷售額估計下降40.3%，零售銷售量可能下降37.5％。零售數據將於收市後公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1585621954419&amp;issue=20200331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1585621954419%26issue%3D20200331&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=5c00d317\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1585621954419&amp;issue=20200331</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ea877dd2f9ca3dadbe0bb27af1af5d6cf6f4f6","tid":1951380,"uid":69886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"成績表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bc6426ae7ac9f2da79a7f602f23a4c247e051b","tid":1951380,"uid":325840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"開始日日都有還押幾個月手足上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1951351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"555b0c62b7465d19861c1e17d920e8f5367513f1","tid":1951380,"uid":997,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy